waiter is not as fun as when I went to Matraman Pratama KPP. Like immediately being kicked out even though I already made an appointment on the visit. He also didn't ask either. I want to make an e-mail, it has been an email, uh, it hasn't been answered for a long time, so I came immediately according to the procedure. He said "yes you have to be online, you can't hurry, we have to take care of lots of people, etc." I have sent the data from Monday to make efin online, and I doubt if I want to take the NPWP card at the same time because I just made it this year. Finally, when I said I wanted to take my NPWP card, I was immediately asked "have you registered online? You have to make an appointment online first". Even though I did make an appointment online according to the date and schedule. Maybe the previous person came angry angry, huh? You know that the office is crowded but why shouldn't I be friendly .. I can write this because I'm from KPP Pratama Matraman and the service is friendly and fast. There it is also conveyed that you can immediately get an EFIN number and NPWP card at the office as long as it matches the regional office according to the NPWP. Why did you say you could be here or not? In the end, I couldn't get the EFIN number when I got home .. yeah, it's okay if I can't get the EFIN number right now, but why was the service at first unfriendly? Don't ask whether it's good for EFIN? Explain, keep asking if there are other needs? This is for one of the fathers of security who is in front, not at the counter. If you don't have a fun day anymore, don't spill it on other people, sir ...<br/><br/>(Original)<br/>Pelayananya gak semenyenangkan kayak pas saya ke KPP Pratama Matraman. Kayak langsung diusir padahal saya udah buat janji di kunjungan.pajak dia juga gak nanya baik baik. Saya mau buat efin sudah email eh lama gak dibales jadi saya dateng langsung udah sesuai prosedur. Dia bilang "ya harus online gak bisa cepet kan kami harus ngurus banyak orang, dll." Saya udah kirim dari senin data untuk buat efin online, dan ragu aja mau sekalian ambil kartu NPWP krn baru bikin tahun ini. Akhirnya pas saya bilang mau ambil krtu NPWP langsung ditanya "sudah daftar online? Harus buat janji dulu online". Padahal emang saya udah janji online sesuai tanggal dan jadwal. Mungkin orang sebelumnya dateng marah marah kali ya? Tau sih kantornya rame tapi kenapa harus gak ramah.. saya bisa nulis gini karna saya dari KPP Pratama Matraman dan disana pelayanannya ramah dan cepet. Disana juga disampaikan bisa langsung dapet nomor EFIN dan kartu NPWP di kantornya asalkan sesuai dengan kantor wilayah sesuai NPWPnya. Kenapa disana bilang bisa disini nggak?
